title: Full servo thermoforming machine US-DH520
title_uz: Bir martalik konteynerlar uchun qopqoq ishlab chiqarish uskunasi US-DH520
title_ru: Оборудование для изготовления крышек одноразовых контейнеров US-DH520
short_description: This US-DH520 equipment produces various containers or cup lids by processing PET and other materials through thermoforming. The maximum size of the manufactured product is 500*320 mm and the maximum width is 520 mm. The weight of the equipment is 2200 kg and its dimensions are 6200*1500*2000 mm.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-DH520 uskuna termo formatsiya orqali PET va boshqa materiallarga ishlov berib har xil konteynerlar yoki stakan qopqoqlarini ishlab chiqaradi. Ishlab chiqariluvchi mahsulotning maksimal o'lchami 500*320 mm va maksimal kengligi 520 mm ni tashkil etadi. Uskunaning vazni 2200 kg va uning o'lchami 6200*1500*2000 mm ni tashkil qiladi.
short_description_ru: Это оборудование US-DH520 производит различные контейнеры или крышки для чашек путем обработки ПЭТ и других материалов методом термоформования. Максимальный размер изготавливаемого изделия 500*320 мм, максимальная ширина 520 мм. Вес оборудования 2200 кг, габариты 6200*1500*2000 мм.
short_description_en: This US-DH520 equipment produces various containers or cup lids by processing PET and other materials through thermoforming. The maximum size of the manufactured product is 500*320 mm and the maximum width is 520 mm. The weight of the equipment is 2200 kg and its dimensions are 6200*1500*2000 mm.
long_description:
This US-DH520 equipment produces various containers or cup lids by processing PET and other materials through thermoforming. The maximum size of the manufactured product is 500*320 mm and the maximum width is 520 mm. The weight of the equipment is 2200 kg and its dimensions are 6200*1500*2000 mm.

 

Basic parameters
Model US-DH520
Suitable sheet PET, PS, PVC
Max. forming area 500*320 mm
Max. width 520 mm
Max. forming width 70 mm
Power 23 kW, 380/220 V
Air pressure 0.6-0.8 Mpa
Capacity 20-30 time/min
Weight 2200 kg
Dimension 6200*1500*2000 mm
long_description_uz:
Ushbu US-DH520 uskuna termo formatsiya orqali PET va boshqa materiallarga ishlov berib har xil konteynerlar yoki stakan qopqoqlarini ishlab chiqaradi. Ishlab chiqariluvchi mahsulotning maksimal o'lchami 500*320 mm va maksimal kengligi 520 mm ni tashkil etadi. Uskunaning vazni 2200 kg va uning o'lchami 6200*1500*2000 mm ni tashkil qiladi.
